NATIONSTAR MORTGAGE, LLC, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Farah Yuceyuksel DONTAS, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Farah Yuceyuksel Dontas, her Heirs, Devisees and Personal Representatives, and her, his, their or any of their Successors in Right, Title and Interest; Erkan S. Yuceyuksel, his Heirs, Devisees and Personal Representatives, and his, her, their or Any of their Successors in Right, Title and Interest; Mrs. Erkan S. Yuceyuksel; Township of Parsippany-Troy Hills; and PNC Bank, Defendants. C-464 September Term 2017
080130 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 12, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002217-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
